Class CONTACTOEMERGENCIA

java.lang.Object
model.CONTACTOEMERGENCIA
public class CONTACTOEMERGENCIA
extends java.lang.Object
Java model for the CONTACTOEMERGENCIA table in the SQL database. Represents a volunteer emergency contact.
